{"tid":1026103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全家過年拜祖先 墳墓垮掉孝子孝孫1死3傷","createTime":"2019-02-18T00:09:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T01:49:38.000Z","uid":150609,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d6a6448db1d7bd978fbd8471faf289a4a8a3b410","tid":1026103,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T00:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7FddOxp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7FddOxp.jpg&h=c50e0a67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國重慶姚姓一家，在過年期間特地去祭拜剛過世的岳父，這墳是才完工10多天的新墳，沒想到，才要燒紙錢，墳墓整個塌陷、墓碑倒下，近千斤重的石塊壓中孝子孝孫，造成1死3傷。<br />\n<br />\n中國重慶一墳墓才完工10天就垮掉，子孫1死3傷。（圖擷取自網路）<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，姚男岳父在今年1月17日下葬，他花了5800元人民幣（約2.64萬台幣），委託工匠為他岳父造墳，才完工10多天，趁著春節假期，在2月4日帶著全家前去祭拜，沒想到，就在準備燒紙錢、放鞭炮的時刻，他突被一塊大石擊中，跌進墳墓邊的溝裡，再回頭一看，整個墳墓都塌陷，包括墓碑、柱子、墳頭（墳墓隆起的部分）一起塌下，近千斤重的石塊接連滾落，全家都被砸重，小孩驚哭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TnjsSY6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTnjsSY6.jpg&h=f5d906b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n姚男拖著骨折的傷腳打電話求救，當地村民將他們一家送到醫院急救，但是，他的太太被砸中頭痛搶救無效死亡，孫子的腳壓傷骨折、女婿的胸都被壓傷。<br />\n<br />\n事後追查，發現是豆腐渣工程惹的禍，整個墳墓工程太隨便，才完工10多就全部垮掉，發生意外。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7054b6e38ad02c6763fe0e7ff67769223ddd6840","tid":1026103,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T00:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90374818ded18c2c1ef68c5500708e56c21c1936","tid":1026103,"uid":186784,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:13:26.000Z","msg":"起墳墓都豆腐渣...垃圾國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89d30bb817f8f03014f574772ca352fe0e9230e","tid":1026103,"uid":125357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568baba0615bfa2d12fe2d1f422baecc1d84d50a","tid":1026103,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:27:03.000Z","msg":"笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不孝子"},{"pid":"375cc943c598498c16f06965b3bceb02f2a52039","tid":1026103,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"568baba0615bfa2d12fe2d1f422baecc1d84d50a","tid":1026103,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:27:03.000Z","msg":"笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不孝子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:35:42.000Z","msg":"肯定出post冇圖"},{"pid":"816244d8988d5a464b4a8c2f3bc4b76184f92b43","tid":1026103,"uid":3189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:35:45.000Z","msg":"屌喇媽<br />\n走去拜山都可以死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咩國家呀"},{"pid":"4da5d47d6dc3e69b867615a95663794809e88abf","tid":1026103,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:36:56.000Z","msg":"祖先顯靈"},{"pid":"2b04650a3331931267f8a7464ce40788d5cad986","tid":1026103,"uid":224815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:39:44.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺"},{"pid":"066c8de5b413e04096789f702d775edcfdb11257","tid":1026103,"uid":31780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:39:53.000Z","msg":"進步咗架喇無喺d石度偷工減料<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490fb41829fc7226c7c5dbe3fef811737b006223","tid":1026103,"uid":35656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:41:06.000Z","msg":"一次過葬埋"},{"pid":"3629c94e6c29d3bd13da4e9c064d97876247a5a8","tid":1026103,"uid":56957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T01:41